nodes.text: A mission to Aut-O's flagship was carried out by the D-Squad to infiltrate a Providence-class carrier/destroyer where an encryption module was held. The D-Squad hacked into C-Deck and made their way to a vault that carried the device. While inside the vault, Aut-O and multiple droids walked in and opened fire. Aut-O was later decapitated by R2-D2. The D-Squad then escaped and made their way back to the Jedi Temple with some difficulties.
